episodes.title: Tell The Whole Story
episodes.author: Myleik Teele
episodes.summary: This podcast is titled “TELL THE WHOLE STORY." Every so often when people write & send a few short facts but typically leave out some very important details … their behavior. I can typically tell when you’re feeding me a few lines of truth and then keeping some important things out because it’s easier to say “everybody at my job is hating on me … what should I do?” Why are they hating on you? I find it hard to believe that EVERYONE is hating on you for NO reason. Don’t debate me on that. I want to be sure that you understand that my perspective isn’t attempt to belittle or call out but to peel back the curtain so that we can both see a clear picture that will allow us to make a couple edits to get on the progressive path. mytaughtyou.com

What lead to Myleik getting a DUI when she was starting her company and how she overcame the criticism she received because of it. How she responds to people who may not like her brutal honesty on social media. What it takes to it to the next level in your life, career and relationships. Why Myleik took 15 vacations last year. Never ASK permission for anything that you shouldn't be. 5. Have fun! 6. Put your PIECES on! 7. If you say something TO or ABOUT someone that would cause them to hit you in your mouth, ask yourself if you would still say if you got hit in it and if you STILL do and get hit, be ready for that too! 8. Next I'm going to get into how fear is educated in and that it can be educated OUT and lastly I'm going to talk about doubt and how that's usually self-inflicted OR the work of the company you keep.
